00:03:04.968 --> 00:03:06.753
We are going to be making some yummy,

00:03:06.753 --> 00:03:09.914
delicious fruit sandwiches.

00:03:09.914 --> 00:03:12.909
I love to eat this before
going out to the gym.

00:03:12.909 --> 00:03:16.164
It's not too heavy, but yet
it gives me that extra boost

00:03:16.164 --> 00:03:18.218
